Description: R package with functions and datasets to support inference with the open access book
            "An Introduction to Bayesian Thinking" 
             <https://statswithr.github.io/book> and the online 
             "Statistics with R Specialization". See <https://github.com/StatsWithR/statsr> for new releases.
